[SN]TITLE[SN]
Alex Iacovitti: Nottingham Forest defender joins Mansfield Town on loan

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Mansfield Town have signed Nottingham Forest defender Alex Iacovitti on a season-long loan.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Iacovitti, 18, made his senior debut for Forest in their 4-3 opening day victory over Burton Albion.
Stags manager Adam Murray bolstered his defensive options after Kyle Howkins suffered an hamstring injury in Tuesday's loss to Doncaster Rovers.
"He's an old-school centre half who can play and has good pace," Murray told the club website.
